data.description: PRICE REDUCED !!!!Beautiful one story level brick home on the North side of Wabash located on the quiet street of Pawling.  Master Suite with large vanity, walk in shower and lots of closet space. 3 Bedrooms, 2 full baths, Living room, Family room, dining room, kitchen, laundry. Attached 2 car garage.  Almost 1800 sq. ft.  The family room has a gas fireplace with insert.   Low yard maintenance, , homeowner has built an L-shaped deck to take care of grilling out and enjoying morning coffee. Newer water heater and kitchen disposal. Roof was new in 2011 , sliding door in 2010. All windows have been professionally caulked, vinyl wrapped and painted to protect the windows. New A/C unit. This home is spacious and open feeling, tastefully decorated!!
